@host = http://127.0.0.1:6000/v1/cats


### Get all cats via id
GET {{host}}/?fields=id&offset=0&limit=2 HTTP/1.1

### Get single cat name
GET {{host}}/6?fields=name HTTP/1.1

### Get all cats with id and name
GET {{host}}/ HTTP/1.1

